<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>shèng líng dài zhe nǐ wǒ zǒu 迦南240</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 shèng líng dài zhe nǐ wǒ zǒu dài zhe nǐ wǒ zǒu wǒ men dōu shuō hǎo bù huí tóu shuō hǎo bù huí tóu
 lì jīng cāng sāng fēng yǔ hòu fēng yǔ hòu nǐ huì fā xiàn zǒu guò de lù yǒu rén yě zài zǒu
 zǒu guò duō shǎo wān fān guò duō shǎo gōu kàn zhe xī yáng xī xià jiāng shuǐ dōng liú
 yàn nán guī xuě huā piāo zǒu guò qù shì gè tiān xiàng qián mò tíng liú</lyrics>
